  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assessment of the adjuvant use Niclosamide With Etanercept in Rheumatoid Arthritis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this randomized double blind placebo-controlled pilot study (Phase I study) we will assess
      the efficacy and safety of adjuvant use Niclosamide With Etanercept in Rheumatoid Arthritis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
